data.description: Wonderful Broadmoor cottage that is perfect for a family.  Upstairs bedroom with additional area is perfect for a playroom or an office.  Large windows across the front of the house allows for plenty of natural light.  Spacious den opens into the formal dining room.  Kitchen has granite tile counter tops, stainless appliances and pass through window.  Beautiful wood floors downstairs.  Landscaped lot with plenty of room to play.
